Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.71,0:23:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧  那邊的同學們
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.73,0:23:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁早跟我來握手

